title: IDM.UltraEdit.v22.0.0.58.Incl.Keymaker-CORE
description:
UltraEdit is the ideal text, HTML and HEX editor, and an advanced PHP,
Perl, Java and JavaScript editor for programmers. An industry-award
winner, UltraEdit supports disk-based 64-bit file handling (standard)
on 32-bit Windows platforms (Windows 2000 and later).
 <a href="
http://www.ultraedit.com/products/ultraedit.html" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">

iNSTALL/REGiSTER NOTES
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

1. Install the application.
2. Patch the hosts file manually.
- Add the following lines to your hosts file in
  WINDOWSsystem32driversetc:
127.0.0.1 licensing.ultraedit.com
127.0.0.1 licensing2.ultraedit.com
3. In menu Help, use activate / offline-activation.
4. Enter anything for license ID and password.
5. Now use keygen to activate the software
